Package: jaciii2025
Title: Viewing Intention Analysis using VAS and FCM
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Naruki", "Shirahama", email = "nshirahama@ieee.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides functions for analyzing Japanese audience data, including clustering, trend analysis, and viewing intention modeling. The package includes a comprehensive manual (jaciii2025.pdf) detailing the methodology and implementation.
